    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >包含第一章（完整版共八章）的故事与战斗，游玩时间约40分钟。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特征 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211040/extras/1c86d0df1c3acf5303f0f91a9a33345a.poster.avif?t=1735294891\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211040/extras/1c86d0df1c3acf5303f0f91a9a33345a.webm?t=1735294891\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211040/extras/1c86d0df1c3acf5303f0f91a9a33345a.mp4?t=1735294891\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>根据你的需求自订难度</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你只想好好读一则故事，还是渴望挑战强大的敌人？本作难度包含「无战斗模式」到「极限模式」，满足不同玩家的需求！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211040/extras/841e6c3a92dddfeb4ae676511c4d2d40.poster.avif?t=1735294891\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211040/extras/841e6c3a92dddfeb4ae676511c4d2d40.webm?t=1735294891\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211040/extras/841e6c3a92dddfeb4ae676511c4d2d40.mp4?t=1735294891\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>不必农的回合制战斗</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >摆脱刷等级、农道具！只要善用伙伴的长处，痛击敌人的弱点，便能克敌制胜！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211040/extras/32a5126bcb44790241d45c86b309351e.poster.avif?t=1735294891\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211040/extras/32a5126bcb44790241d45c86b309351e.webm?t=1735294891\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211040/extras/32a5126bcb44790241d45c86b309351e.mp4?t=1735294891\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>2.5D运镜・临场感十足</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >采用2.5D运镜，使叙事更有临场感。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >人物 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211040/extras/ca6dc5336376f54ef7b79fdf05d7fd8f.avif?t=1735294891\" width=608 height=342 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211040/extras/b8f7ee0a5c76e6c57bdc03f750432bc8.avif?t=1735294891\" width=608 height=342 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211040/extras/3ce0a83ba256f21278443b30d0f9a043.avif?t=1735294891\" width=608 height=342 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211040/extras/5595a61b4840de49be827827fa3ceb21.avif?t=1735294891\" width=608 height=342 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >直播与游戏实况之规范</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >允许直播与游戏实况。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >允许营利，但仅限于以影音网站的功能营利。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >若能在直播或游戏实况的标题加入游戏名称，或在说明栏列出Steam页面的连结，我方将不胜感激。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >直播与游戏实况所导致的任何损害，我方概不负责。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本规范如有变更，恕不另行通知。</p></li></ul>",
